data.description: Nice location with a cute Cottage & a private fenced in back yard. Built in 1954 with approximately 720 square feet this 2 bedroom / 1 bathroom home is vacant and ready for new owners.  Has a newer composition roof, vinyl windows, Kitchen has oak cabinets with range, refrigerator and built-in dishwasher included. Convenient location for the laundry area off the kitchen. Covered back porch area, lot is approximately 45 X 120 & includes an attached Carport.
